## 1. What This App Is

Al Farasha Sales Ledger is a **fully self-contained, single HTML file** that functions as a complete business accounting and sales management system for a building materials trading company in Sharjah, UAE.

It is designed specifically for the way this business operates — a **dispatch-and-shop hybrid** model where salesmen carry goods out on delivery (dispatch) and a retail shop also sells directly to walk-in customers. The app manages:

- Customer accounts and credit ledgers
- Sales invoices (with optional VAT 5%)
- Payment collection tracking
- Daily dispatch (van loading / stock tracking)
- Customer account statements (English and Urdu)
- Notifications for overdue accounts and credit limits

The entire app lives in **one HTML file** — no backend server, no npm, no build step. Open it in a browser and it works. When installed as a PWA, it becomes a native-like app on any phone or desktop.

