### The Special Cash Sale Customer

A built-in virtual customer with a fixed ID `CASH_SALE_ID = 'CASH_SALE_ENTITY'` is always present in the database. This represents walk-in cash customers. It is:

- Created automatically via `ensureCashSaleCustomer()` on every app start and on every Firebase sync
- Never deletable or renameable
- Excluded from duplicate invoice checking (walk-ins can buy the same things on the same day)
- Shown with a "Cash" tag in all dropdowns
- Always treated as paid in full at time of sale

### Unique ID Generation

```javascript
function uid() {
  return 'id' + Date.now().toString(36) + Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 7);
}
```

IDs are URL-safe strings combining a timestamp (base-36) and random suffix — collision-proof without requiring a backend.

