## 21. Print System

### Print Targets

Only elements with class `.print-target` are visible when printing. Everything else is `visibility: hidden`.

### Statement Print

The statement document lives inside the app shell and uses `position: static`. On print, the app shell is preserved but non-statement elements are hidden.

### Invoice Print

Invoice preview lives in a `position: fixed` overlay. Printing requires the overlay to become `position: static` and the app shell behind it to be `display: none` — otherwise both the invoice and the app content behind it would print.

### Preventing Blank Pages

Every `min-height`, `height: 100vh`, and `overflow` on `html`, `body`, `#app-shell`, and `#main` is neutralized in `@media print` to prevent trailing blank pages.

